.SH SAFETY
cleanix never deletes protected system paths or a user's home, credential, or media directories, never follows a symlink to delete its target, and runs external commands without a shell. Use \fB\-\-quarantine\fR for reversible removal and \fB\-\-simulate\fR to preview the exact target list.
